description:
Title Passive electronic components
Author Gayan Roshantha
Pages 112

Passive electronic components, such as resistors, inductors, capacitors, or
transformers, do not require any source of energy to perform their function in
an application.

In this presentation i mainly explain about

* Capacitors
* Coils, Inductors
* Resistors


i also added some working examples and solutions. Have a look and gain your knowledge.
